Class ImageDirectoryProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.exec.store.image.ImageDirectoryProcessor

  • public class ImageDirectoryProcessor
extends Object
    Although each image format can contain different metadata, they also have common basic information. The class handles basic metadata as well as complex tags.
